## TRMNL Plugin Licensing

By publishing this plugin (hereinafter "Work") as a TRMNL Recipe, the Creator
agrees to the TRMNL Plugin Licensing terms:

### General Use

1. Visual design, data parsing logic, and markup shall conform to Creative
   Commons "CC-BY 4.0" terms:
   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
2. End-users may contact Creator for support.
3. Best efforts will be made to sustain functionality for any number of
   connections with up to 5 minute refresh intervals.
4. Work may be removed, unlisted, or transferred to the TRMNL team due to
   persistent malfunction or Creator non-responsiveness. Creator may reclaim
   this Work by contacting the TRMNL team and resuming maintenance
   responsibilities.

### Exceptions

1. If Work cannot sustain active connections or refresh rates, TRMNL may allow
   rate limits and connection throttling, or higher payload limits than
   documented.
2. If TRMNL receives legal notice (e.g. DMCA takedown request), Work may be
   de-listed despite satisfactory functionality.

